OL,3,CMan seriously injured in town centre
OL,4,Cpark stabbing
OL,6,FA man has been left with significant
OL,7,Finjuries after he was stabbed in
OL,8,FSussex.
OL,10,FPolice are investigating a report that
OL,11,Fhe was attacked in Victoria Park,
OL,12,FWorthing at around 2.45am on Saturday,
OL,13,F28 February.
OL,15,FTwo men were reported to have attacked
OL,16,Fthe victim after a brief interaction
OL,17,Fin the park.
OL,19,FHe was immediately taken to hospital
OL,20,Fand remains there in a stable
OL,21,Fcondition at this time.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/2
