PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1772447793
OL,3,CMan seriously injured in town centre
OL,4,Cpark stabbing
OL,6,FThe suspects are described as
OL,7,Fapproximately between 20 and 30-years-
OL,8,Fold, white, and wearing grey
OL,9,Ftracksuits with their hoods up and
OL,10,Ffaces covered.
OL,12,FDetective Sergeant Harry Mansbridge,
OL,13,Fsaid: "Officers are carrying out a
OL,14,Fnumber of enquiries in the area to
OL,15,Festablish exactly what happened, and
OL,16,Fto identify who is responsible.
OL,18,F"We are asking anyone with relevant
OL,19,Ffootage or information to get in touch.
OL,21,F"Any information could be key."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/2
